4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of CNNs for camera relocalisation and map compression can be seen as an application of artificial intelligence. Hence, cs.AI is a possible sub-category. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics): While not the most likely sub-category, cs.GR is a possibility as the paper deals with camera relocalisation, which is relevant to computer graphics applications such as augmented reality and virtual reality.
